# Authors

This file lists significant contributors to the project. It is not exhaustive
— see `git log --format='%aN <%aE>' | sort -u` for the full contributor list.

The presence of a name here indicates copyright attribution for a substantial
contribution (a new skill, protocol, theme preset, or architectural module
larger than ~100 lines). Smaller fixes and improvements are equally welcome
and recorded in the git history.

## Project lead

- Michael Boiman <mboiman@bks-lab.com> — original author, architect, maintainer

